As of 7 Aug 2022, Nepal has administered 53 260 490 doses of the COVID-19 vaccine (https://covid19.who.int/region/searo/country/np).

Sri Lanka has administered at least 39 724 661 doses of the COVID-19 vaccine as of 7 Aug 2022 (https://covid19.who.int/region/searo/country/lk).

